A Nigerian man identified as Rabiu Biyora, blurred his bride’s face in their pre-wedding photo posted along with the invites. Rabiu who is a member of Situation Room President Muhammadu Buhari Campaign Office Kano 2019, on Saturday posted invites to his wedding set to hold on Sunday, January 5 in Adamawa. The post Nigerian man blurs his wife-to-be’s face in prewedding photo as he announces their wedding date appeared first on YabaLeftOnline. Source: Yaba Left